<h2
  style="
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  "
>
  You're invited to join ChatFlex
</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #334155; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6">
  Hello <strong style="color: #0f172a"><%= name %></strong>,
</p>

<div
  style="
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 12px;
  "
>
  <p
    style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #334155; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6"
  >
    <strong style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 17px"><%= inviterName %></strong>
    has invited you to join
    <strong style="color: #0f172a"><%= workspaceName %></strong> as
    <span
      style="
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 2px 10px;
        background: #e0f2f1;
        color: #0f766e;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 20px;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      "
      ><%= role %></span
    >.
  </p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #334155; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6">
  Click the button below to accept the invitation and complete account setup.
  This gives you access to your new workspace and all its features.
</p>

<table
  role="presentation"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  style="margin: 0 0 24px"
  width="100%"
>
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <table
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        style="display: inline-block"
      >
        <tr>
          <td
            align="center"
            style="
              border-radius: 12px;
              background: #0f766e;
              box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.2);
            "
          >
            <a
              href="<%= invitationUrl %>"
              style="
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 14px 32px;
                color: #ffffff;
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-decoration: none;
                line-height: 1;
                border-radius: 12px;
                background: #0f766e;
              "
              >Accept Invitation →</a
            >
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<div
  style="
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 16px;
    background: #fff7ed;
    border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
    border-radius: 8px;
  "
>
  <p style="margin: 0; color: #7b341e; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5">
    ⚡ This invitation link will expire in <strong>72 hours</strong> for
    security reasons.
  </p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6">
  Having trouble with the button? Copy and paste this link into your browser:
</p>

<table
  role="presentation"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  style="margin: 0 0 16px"
  width="100%"
>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="
        padding: 12px 16px;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        word-break: break-all;
      "
    >
      <a
        href="<%= invitationUrl %>"
        style="
          color: #0f766e;
          font-size: 14px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-family: monospace;
        "
        ><%= invitationUrl %></a
      >
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<hr style="margin: 32px 0 24px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0" />

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5">
  <strong style="color: #334155">Didn't expect this invitation?</strong> You can
  safely ignore this email. Only people with access to this email address can
  accept the invitation.
</p>
<p style="margin: 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5">
  Questions? Visit our
  <a href="#" style="color: #0f766e; text-decoration: underline">Help Center</a>
  or contact support.
</p>
